OL,3,CFormer mayor of Liverpool and 11
OL,4,Cothers to appear in court
OL,6,FFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson is
OL,7,Fdue to appear in court after being
OL,8,Fcharged with bribery and misconduct in
OL,9,Fa public office.
OL,11,FThe 67-year-old was first arrested in
OL,12,FDecember 2020 and is among 11 others
OL,13,Fappear at Preston Crown Court
OL,14,Ffollowing a corruption investigation.
OL,16,FOperation Aloft, carried out by
OL,17,FMerseyside Police, was an
OL,18,Finvestigation focussed on the awarding
OL,19,Fof commercial and business contracts
OL,20,Fby Liverpool City Council between 2010
OL,21,Fand 2020.
