OL,3,CFormer mayor of Liverpool and 11
OL,4,Cothers to appear in court
OL,6,FAnderson, of Knotty Ash in Liverpool,
OL,7,Fwas suspended by the Labour Party
OL,8,Ffollowing his arrest in 2020 and did
OL,9,Fnot stand for re-election the
OL,10,Ffollowing year for the role of Mayor,
OL,11,Fwhich he had held since 2012.
OL,13,FThe council's ex-deputy leader Derek
OL,14,FHatton, 77, will appear before
OL,15,Fmagistrates today.
OL,17,FHatton, of Aigburth, Liverpool has
OL,18,Fbeen charged with one count of bribery
OL,19,Fand one count of counselling or
OL,20,Fprocuring misconduct in a public
OL,21,Foffice.
